				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Phong-t%E1%BA%ADt-chu-trung-ph%E1%BB%A5c-ch%E1%BA%A9m-th%C6%B0-ho%C3%A0i-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-l%E1%BB%A5c-v%E1%BA%ADn-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%93-Nam-th%C3%A2n-h%E1%BB%AFu/poem-maRxAMOCboIbSdvxXl781Q">Phong tật chu trung phục chẩm thư hoài tam thập lục vận, phụng trình Hồ Nam thân hữu - 風疾舟中伏枕書懷三十六韻，奉呈湖南親友</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu%E1%BB%B7-t%C3%BAc-khi%E1%BB%83n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-tr%C3%ACnh-qu%E1%BA%A7n-c%C3%B4ng/poem-x2D4zVhf9YbxgypolcKI9w">Thuỷ túc khiển hứng phụng trình quần công - 水宿遣興奉呈群公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-m%E1%BA%A1n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-k%E1%BB%B3-7/poem--uIN8ncvnQv_ihgIj7uLfA">Tuyệt cú mạn hứng kỳ 7 - 絕句漫興其七</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-T%C3%A2y-H%E1%BB%93-k%C3%BD-T%E1%BA%A1-ph%C3%A1p-t%C3%A0o-ca/poem-z3c3Uy-4hhaCaIjhx-Cqvw">Xuân nhật Tây Hồ ký Tạ pháp tào ca - 春日西湖寄謝法曹歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/author-Rh6zapU4AwLAuhG1Xl_FMw">Âu Dương Tu</a>)<br></div>	</div>
